detailIntroText: Pixels is a captivating, open-ended world of farming and exploration, built one pixel at a time. Gather resources, develop skills, and form relationships as you explore the story and quests within the Pixels Universe. You will be immersed in a mesmerizing mix of managing, creating, and exploring in a world that combines blockchain ownership with your progression and achievements.
introduceText: Open-ended world of farming and exploration
